  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are a wild horse in the wild west! That's it . . . that's the game!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ROAM is an  silly sandbox game where you play as a wild horse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✮ ✮ ✮ <strong>GAME FEATURES </strong>✮ ✮ ✮</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customize your horse and herd!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The detailed horse editor allows you to create fun, unique horses! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Choose their ages, genders, names, and appearances and build the horse family of your dreams!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/a44e8d2d4ff7b66ad123da55f6b8c907.poster.avif?t=1733159498\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/a44e8d2d4ff7b66ad123da55f6b8c907.webm?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/a44e8d2d4ff7b66ad123da55f6b8c907.mp4?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Expand your herd by rescuing captured horses and by breeding your horses!</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Breed your horses to create unique foals and watch them grow up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Rescue other horses in the world and free them from the townsfolk!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/7de521e52ca0e8697148aa2d9c1c0381.poster.avif?t=1733159498\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/7de521e52ca0e8697148aa2d9c1c0381.webm?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/7de521e52ca0e8697148aa2d9c1c0381.mp4?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take care of your horse and your herd!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• The horses have hunger and energy needs! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Find your herd a safe oasis where they (and you) can relax and eat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/000c17ec6ef357e8dc02916bf9f02bb4.poster.avif?t=1733159498\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/000c17ec6ef357e8dc02916bf9f02bb4.webm?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/000c17ec6ef357e8dc02916bf9f02bb4.mp4?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play as any of your horses using the horse-switch feature! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/dd74fcca15a0426f358196a788e7cd62.poster.avif?t=1733159498\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/dd74fcca15a0426f358196a788e7cd62.webm?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/dd74fcca15a0426f358196a788e7cd62.mp4?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cause havoc in the local towns - but try to avoid being captured!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• You can attack the local townsfolk if you feel like causing some chaos!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Try to avoid being captured! If you are, you will need to escape - and the townsfolk won't make it easy for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/9d5126b498fe44b03a2b661bb385e27e.poster.avif?t=1733159498\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/9d5126b498fe44b03a2b661bb385e27e.webm?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208940/extras/9d5126b498fe44b03a2b661bb385e27e.mp4?t=1733159498\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
